Bob Diamond may refer to:

People

*Bob Diamond (banker), an American banker
*Bobby Diamond, California lawyer who was a child star and young-adult actor of the 1950s and 1960s
*Bobby Dimond, Australian rugby league footballer of the 1940s and 1950s

Fictional characters

*Bob Diamond (comics), a Marvel Comics character
*Bob Diamond, an advocate in the movie Defending Your Life
